data.title: Library of Congress Finding Aids: Browse by Name
data.meta_description: Browse LC finding aids by names and titles. Finding aids are XML documents created using the Encoded Archival Description (EAD). Names and titles associated with finding aids. Includes collection titles, entries for significant works contained in collections, and entries for significant works discussed in collections.
